you want to handle,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then choose a redirect method. The context will fire the completion handler"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the redirect completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Due to the nature of iOS, very little concrete information can be gained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"during this process, as all actions take place in either the Safari app","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or the sandboxed SFSafariViewController class. The context attempts to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detect when the user has completed the necessary redirect action by listening","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for both app foregrounds and url callbacks received in the app delegate."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, it is possible the when the redirect is “completed”, the user may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have not actually completed the necessary actions to authorize the charge."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"You should not use either this class, nor "},{"code":"STPAPIClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", as a way"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to determine when you should charge the Source or to determine if the redirect"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was successful. Use Stripe webhooks on your backend server to listen for Source"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"state changes and to make the charge."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"STPRedirectContext","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/stripepaymentsui\/stpredirectcontext","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.stripe.stripe-payments-ui/documentation/StripePaymentsUI":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments-ui\/documentation\/StripePaymentsUI","type":"topic","role":"collection","title"